name: Icensmis
tagline: Study Design and Data Analysis in the Presence of Error-Prone Diagnostic Tests and Self-Reported Outcomes
body: ## icensmis This is an R package for Study Design and Data Analysis in the Presence of Error-Prone Diagnostic Tests and Self-Reported Outcomes. Please refer to our Annals of Applied Statistics paper and Statistics in Medicine paper for more details of proposed methods.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
